75
00:08:59,416 --> 00:09:07,625
So the soul never dies, the soul leaves one body and immediately joins another body, then those who attain salvation

76
00:09:07,708 --> 00:09:11,916
that is the only body that goes to Lord Vishnu

77
00:09:14,208 --> 00:09:17,000
Attainment of salvation comes directly from Lord Vishnu.

78
00:09:17,041 --> 00:09:27,333
