117
00:13:51,208 --> 00:13:56,083
I have gone till Shillong, I have gone till Brahmakamal

118
00:13:58,458 --> 00:14:01,583
At that time I found 5365 sadhus

119
00:14:04,083 --> 00:14:05,208
abbot people

120
00:14:05,583 --> 00:14:09,083
But among them I understood only three people, that three are right and the rest are useless.

121
00:14:09,250 --> 00:14:11,041
Interviewer: How did you shortlist these guys?

122
00:14:11,083 --> 00:14:14,666
We have seen them, we just sit while talking.

123
00:14:16,458 --> 00:14:22,458
Wherever satsang is going on, sadhus are sitting there, we also sit in the middle, listening.

124
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:29,500
I asked anyone, whatever my soul said and I did not get the right answer.

125
00:14:31,541 --> 00:14:42,541
Later I saw that he was lying somewhere after drinking alcohol, someone was lying here after consuming cannabis and was saying that you give us something, I will order this, I will order that.

126
00:14:42,958 --> 00:14:43,625
so what is all this

127
00:14:45,083 --> 00:14:51,750
We found such and such people, but I found three saints, who were a little good, and even those were not complete.

128
00:14:53,458 --> 00:14:58,500
Means the one with half paisa, the same form of 12 year old that was mentioned in the beginning.

129
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:09,208
Look, in front of us was an indifferent Indradev, he was doing penance for 12 years at the doorstep of Vishwanath temple in Uttarkashi.

130
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:20,250
From 12 years, only one day was left, just 12 hours and in 12 hours his 12 years of penance was broken

131
00:15:22,125 --> 00:15:24,750
He was fascinated by a girl

132
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:33,250
Maya got into his head, she was a girl from Germany, he got fascinated, he married her.

133
00:15:35,458 --> 00:15:42,916
After a week she returned from Germany after selling her entire property,

134
00:15:42,958 --> 00:15:48,250
And the moment he saw that Maya had taken over his head, he killed her, tied her in a bundle and threw her in the Ganga.

135
00:15:49,916 --> 00:15:51,166
so there are such saints

136
00:15:55,250 --> 00:16:05,625
We came face to face with him, where the sages live, where ever the place is set, there is smoke and the smoke should keep burning for 24 hours.

137
00:16:07,541 --> 00:16:11,500
If one belongs to Naga sect then the incense stick should be kept burning for 24 hours.

138
00:16:12,083 --> 00:16:17,125
We saw that the smoke was cold, we said Maharaj, tell us one thing.

139
00:16:18,625 --> 00:16:27,791
Your age is around 50-62. He said yes, I said how long have you been a saint?  They said it's been 42 years for me

140
00:16:28,333 --> 00:16:35,333
