143
00:16:53,666 --> 00:17:02,083
I said, Maharaj, from where you became a saint, I said, I am the guru of that Akhara, I am from Khadakhara Akhara.

144
00:17:02,541 --> 00:17:04,250
Find where is Khadakhada Akhara

145
00:17:06,208 --> 00:17:08,791
search search worldwide

146
00:17:11,125 --> 00:17:12,250
nothing will be found

147
00:17:18,791 --> 00:17:23,541
And later when he got worried, he started asking, Maharaj, where is this Kharakha Akhara?

148
00:17:24,375 --> 00:17:34,208
We said, this is a cremation ground, this is a crematorium, Harishchandra was sitting in the ghat and said, look, this is a ghat, it runs 24 hours, this is a crematorium, you are blind.

149
00:17:36,375 --> 00:17:39,625
You have not opened the eyes here, you have just kept this one open.

150
00:17:41,583 --> 00:17:43,375
from which only illusion is visible

151
00:17:45,791 --> 00:17:47,541
only illusion is visible

152
00:17:49,333 --> 00:17:53,791
The truth is not visible, and it is a permanent arena that runs 24 hours a day.

153
00:17:55,916 --> 00:17:57,333
I belong to that arena

154
00:17:58,833 --> 00:18:06,000
He started looking at me from top to bottom, I said go have fun, go, ask, eat and have fun but don't fool me.

155
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:14,875
Interviewer: Baba, there are some sadhus who worship dead bodies. What is the difference between them and sadhus?

156
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:21,375
baba: Now they are Aghori, those who are Aghori are Kapalik.

157
00:18:22,250 --> 00:18:28,083
Those who are Kapalikas worship the dead and awaken them.

158
00:18:28,416 --> 00:18:28,833
interviewer: why

159
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:34,916
baba: For some Tantra Vidya, which is called magic power, black magic.

160
00:18:38,875 --> 00:18:45,375
Like I embezzled something of yours and gave it to them, embezzled theirs and gave it to them, embezzled theirs and gave it to them, so what is all this black magic?

161
00:18:47,125 --> 00:18:50,583
exorcising, soaking, burdening, burdensome work

162
00:18:51,750 --> 00:18:57,500
So this used to be their job but not everyone does it, some are such wise that they follow the truth.

163
00:18:58,583 --> 00:19:05,333
But here it is mostly untrue, the truth is not visible, it just dominates.

164
00:19:06,166 --> 00:19:07,166
Interviewer: Is it all a pretense?

165
00:19:09,458 --> 00:19:11,375
baba: Yes, Keenaram was a person

166
00:19:13,625 --> 00:19:15,791
His last generation was Yavdutram

167
00:19:17,333 --> 00:19:26,000
If Yavdutram had followed the rules then this yavdutram would have been the 21st generation of Keenaram.

168
00:19:26,541 --> 00:19:28,708
Interviewer: Can an Aghori hurt anyone?
baba: yes

169
00:19:31,041 --> 00:19:35,500
Interviewer: What would be the motive of Aghori, what would be his aim to hurt someone?

170
00:19:35,541 --> 00:19:43,125
baba: It is like that if someone has done such a deed to him then he can hurt him, that too through his Tantra Kriya.

171
00:19:45,125 --> 00:19:46,875
whatever he says will happen

172
00:19:49,333 --> 00:19:50,791
Interviewer: They have so much power

173
00:19:51,083 --> 00:19:56,291
baba: But not everyone, maybe one in a million is like this.

174
00:19:57,541 --> 00:19:58,666
Interviewer: How different are they from saints?

175
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:05,541
These people live 10 miles apart from the saints, 10 miles

176
00:20:08,208 --> 00:20:15,958
Because Avaguni Tantra is the 44th part of Lord Shankar.

177
00:20:18,166 --> 00:20:20,666
Like Lord Shankar always stays in the crematorium

178
00:20:23,666 --> 00:20:28,750
The 44th part is Aghor Tantra, not everyone does that.

179
00:20:31,583 --> 00:20:36,750
There are 44 types of Aghoris also.

180
00:20:38,083 --> 00:20:48,083
Some people perform the cremation rituals, some people perform the rituals while sitting in the graveyard, some people perform the rituals while sitting in water, all the rituals are of the crematorium only.

181
00:20:51,041 --> 00:20:52,458
So these are the three ways

182
00:20:55,125 --> 00:21:00,083
The fourth one is where people are buried in the cemetery.

183
00:21:02,791 --> 00:21:05,333
So all these are the same rituals of cremation but all are different.

184
00:21:06,250 --> 00:21:09,916
Everyone's work is divided that you have to do this, you have to do this, you have to do this

185
00:21:09,958 --> 00:21:13,250
Interviewer: Whom do these Aghori worship?

186
00:21:14,166 --> 00:21:23,833
baba: Worship Mahakaal, worship Kali, worship Mahakali, that's it, nothing else, worship skeleton Kali.

